This is a maven Project.
Using Testng Listeners
Class Level Listeners used in "ClassListenersDemo.java" class
Suite Level Listeners used in SuiteListenerDemo

How to take screenshot and how to use that in the listeners..
Takescreenshot code in base class here.

When the test fails then it will take the screenshot and save in the particular folder(which you give the folder path).
Screenshot will be saved in the .png format with the name of testmethod along with the system timestamp as the below mentioned format.
"<methodname>_yyyy-mm-dd HH-mm-ss.png"


screenShot

When ever we use Listeners then it will generate a report in testng results file in html format with the name of test name under the name of suitename folder.


